p
\sum_{i_1, \ldots, i_p=1}^n \frac{\partial^{2p}}{\partial x_{i_1}^2\ldots \partial x_{i_p}^2}f(x, \xi),
\mathcal{L}_x
x
f
p
\left(\sum_{i=1}^n x_i\right)^p=\sum_{|\alpha|=p}\frac{p!}{\alpha!}x^\alpha. 
\mathcal{L}_x=\sum_{i=1}^n \frac{\partial^2}{\partial x_i^2},
\mathcal{L}_x^p=\left(\sum_{i=1}^n \frac{\partial^2}{\partial x_i^2}\right)^p=\sum_{|\alpha|=p}\frac{p!}{\alpha!}\partial^{2\alpha}_x,
\displaystyle \partial^{2\alpha}_x=\partial_{x_1}^{2\alpha_1}\cdots \partial_{x_n}^{2\alpha_n}=\frac{\partial^{2|\alpha|}}{\partial x_1^{2\alpha_1}\cdots \partial x_n^{2\alpha_n}}.
